  <!-- ── 8. Section 5: Reporting gap ─────────────────────────────────── -->
  <section id="reporting-gap" class="py-16 bg-[#F8F7FA] border-b border-[#0A0F1E]/8">
    <div class="max-w-4xl mx-auto px-6">
      <h2 class="text-2xl md:text-3xl font-bold tracking-tight text-ink leading-tight mb-4">5. The reporting gap is the largest single problem in US fraud data</h2>
      <div class="prose prose-lg text-body max-w-none space-y-6 text-[21px] leading-[1.7] mb-8">
        <p>Every number in this report is built on top of a reporting layer that captures a small fraction of actual fraud activity.</p>
      </div>

      <div class="overflow-x-auto bg-white rounded-2xl border border-[#0A0F1E]/8">
        <table class="w-full text-sm text-left">
          <thead>
            <tr class="border-b border-[#0A0F1E]/8 bg-[#F8F7FA]">
